snippet.title: Planet of Lana - Game Pass & Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Planet of Lana will be available day one with Xbox Game Pass & PC Game Pass!

Release set to Spring 2023! Thanks for all love & support and hope you can have some more patience before getting to experience Lana & Mui’s epic adventure. 

Wishlist on Steam: bit.ly/PlanetOfLana 
Newsletter to get news about the upcoming release: https://bit.ly/3MtYmlB
